    "lore": "Many uncanny war engines have emerged from the forges of the Clans Skryre, but the Doomwheels are arguably the most bizarre. These contraptions can appear almost amusing to incredulous foes; resembling giant wheels, they roll forwards at an unsteady pace. Yet amusement gives way to terror as the Doomwheel picks up speed, erratic blasts of warp lightning leaping from the ruinous realmstone crystals affixed to prongs on its flanks. Any caught in its path will be either blasted to blackened corpses or simply ground to bloody smears.",
