    "lore": "Plague Furnaces are mobile altars of corruption, rotting pulpits from which priests of the Pestilent Brotherhood can preach the Withered Word. Pushed by toiling packs of Plague Monks, a Plague Furnace is a ponderous construct. Its decay-eaten structure creaks and whines as it rolls forwards on grinding wheels, while thick clouds of toxic smoke emanate from the censer at its heart. This is no ordinary gas; it is laced not only with warpstone but also with the gurgled incantations of the Plague Priest who commands the Furnace.",
