    "lore": "Plague Monks form the foetid congregations of the Clans Pestilens. Though inherently cowardly in the manner of all Skaven, on the battlefield, they are seized by a zealous fervour that is both bizarre and extremely unnerving to behold. Clad solely in fly-eaten robes and carrying all manner of strange religious paraphernalia and relics, they surge forwards like a mouldering landslide. Driven on by their rabid mania, they swarm against the ranks of the enemy, lashing out in a furore with blades and withered staves.",
