    "name": "Eyes of the Nine",
    "subname": null,
    "lore": "Vortemis has been instrumental in twisting the strands of fate to serve the will of Tzeentch. His Arcanite Cult had spies in the city of Shadespire for centuries, and he has plotted to undermine Nagash for just as long. Agents of the Gaunt Summoners, the Eyes of the Nine seek out artefacts redolent with realm magics that they can corrupt with Tzeentchian energy. With these ensorcelled lodestones, they intend to tether the Silver Towers to reality.",
