    "lore": "Carried upon buzzing insectile wings, an Emerald Lifeswarm embodies Ghyran’s healing powers. They are conjured from the remnants of life, be it a forlorn tree husk or a mouldering corpse. Seeking out those wounded unto death, a Lifeswarm descends to meld with torn tissue and reknit organs and bones. Yet all things are cyclical, and renewal is entwined with death. A Lifeswarm seeks out foes as eagerly as it does friends, but to these it delivers countless poisonous bites, burrowing inside armour to strike where they are most vulnerable.",
