    "lore": "Gotrek Gurnisson hails from a world lost to legend. After a great shame befell him, he swore an oath to meet an honourable death in battle – but with his warrior skill and the unwelcome favour of the fallen god Grimnir, no foe has yet proven equal to the task. Cantankerous, surly and stubborn to a fault, Gotrek is ever travelling across the realms in search of battle. For a worthy cause, he might lend his axe for a time; still, allies are wise to keep out of the Slayer’s business, if they know what’s good for them.",
