    "lore": "Horrorghasts are summoned by necromantic rituals or mass sacrifice. They have no form of their own, appearing as whatever will most terrify their prey, feeding off their panic and billowing it back out in a withering miasma of doom. Though most commonly encountered roaming the bleak wilds of Shyish, the battlefield offers much of a Horrorghast’s favoured sustenance. While Horrorghasts have been recorded as taking all manner of forms, there are few mortals who do not fear death, and so many manifest as the distorted visage of the Great Necromancer himself.",
