    "lore": "Unlike most Skaven warriors, who tend towards being stooped and rangy, Stormvermin are immediately identifiable by their comparative bulk and general aura of menace. Hand-picked from the most promising spawn of a litter – usually marked by having devoured many of their brood-mates – they are subjected to especially brutal training regimes by their Clawlords. This results in ratmen that are able to fight with a degree of precision and focus uncommon to their kin.",
