    "lore": "Clawlords command from the very back ranks - the most honourable of all positions within Skaven society. After all, why should a leader sully their own blade with violence when there are plenty of minions able to die on their behalf? Clawlords expend the lives of their underlings freely, safe in the knowledge that there are always more where they came from. The wisest amongst them also make sure that they always have an escape route to paw - even if they must cut through enemies and allies alike in the process.",
