    "lore": "Within the voluminous barrel of a Warpfire Thrower sloshes a particularly incendiary and evil concoction. When the Skaven gunner depresses a trigger, this liquid is fed through crude piping to spew out of a brass nozzle, igniting on contact with the air to produce sheets of blinding green flame. So deadly is this compound that it cannot be doused through conventional means; those whom it strikes can only burn to death in agony as the fire leaps across tightly packed ranks of infantry.",
